  "detailed_description": "<strong><u>Game History:</u></strong><br><br>After his daughter passed away, a painful silence wanders through the cold hallways, letting the nasty feelings of guilt free. The only way to get closer to his daughter is through a birthday gift, the little doll she loved so much.<br><br>You're Frank Walker, a man devastated by the awful experiences that left a mark in your mental health.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every time you play is a different experience</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/d80419b5b036f7110d6501731971d95b.poster.avif?t=1684660470\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/d80419b5b036f7110d6501731971d95b.webm?t=1684660470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/d80419b5b036f7110d6501731971d95b.mp4?t=1684660470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The re-playability of 'Find Me' and its aleatory features make every time you play a different experience, terrifying and unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't let them find you</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/ed06651ec4318f66bf1ed1e5e21147dc.poster.avif?t=1684660470\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/ed06651ec4318f66bf1ed1e5e21147dc.webm?t=1684660470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/ed06651ec4318f66bf1ed1e5e21147dc.mp4?t=1684660470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you want to survive, you can use the several hideouts spread all over the map, but you have to remember not to let them see you while you're about to hide.<br><i>(Hideouts improved with the v1.0 update)</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><u>Game History:</u></strong><br><br>After his daughter passed away, a painful silence wanders through the cold hallways, letting the nasty feelings of guilt free. The only way to get closer to his daughter is through a birthday gift, the little doll she loved so much.<br><br>You're Frank Walker, a man devastated by the awful experiences that left a mark in your mental health.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every time you play is a different experience</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/d80419b5b036f7110d6501731971d95b.poster.avif?t=1684660470\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/d80419b5b036f7110d6501731971d95b.webm?t=1684660470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/d80419b5b036f7110d6501731971d95b.mp4?t=1684660470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The re-playability of 'Find Me' and its aleatory features make every time you play a different experience, terrifying and unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't let them find you</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/ed06651ec4318f66bf1ed1e5e21147dc.poster.avif?t=1684660470\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/ed06651ec4318f66bf1ed1e5e21147dc.webm?t=1684660470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211420/extras/ed06651ec4318f66bf1ed1e5e21147dc.mp4?t=1684660470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you want to survive, you can use the several hideouts spread all over the map, but you have to remember not to let them see you while you're about to hide.<br><i>(Hideouts improved with the v1.0 update)</i>",
